<div class="sec-6-wrapper section">
    <h1 class="slided-out transition-transform" id="sec-6-title">Multiple touches rule</h1>
    <p class="slided-out transition-transform" id="sec-6-par-1">Here is where things get interesting. Unlike in volleyball, a player is allowed to touch the ball multiple times, as long as the ball isn't held still of course.</p>
    <p class="slided-out transition-transform" id="sec-6-par-2">This special rule allows players to develop advanced tecniques and tactics.</p>
</div>